-- Raven Russia Considers $1 Billion Moscow Property-Bond Sale, Times Reports
-- B y   A g n e s   L o v a s z
-- 2010-09-26T08:36:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-26/raven-russia-considers-1-billion-moscow-property-bond-sale-times-reports.html
Raven Russia , a London-listed
property company founded by  Anton Bilton , is talking to banks
about a $1 billion sale of bonds backed rental income from real-
estate holdings in Moscow and St. Petersburg, the Sunday Times
reported, without saying how it got the information.  To contact the reporters on this story:
